#. Tag: title
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "OPIS"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kpatience; is a compendium of several well known patience card games, "
"ranging from the well known Klondike and Freecell, to lesser known games "
"such as Grandfather's Clock and Mod3. In all there are 12 variations for you "
"to while away time."
msgstr ""
"&kpatience; je zbirka več dobro znanih iger potrpežljivosti s kartami, od "
"znanih Klondike in Freecell do manj znanih iger, kot sta Dedkova ura in "
"Mod3. Skupaj je na voljo 12 različic, s katerimi lahko ubijate čas."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "OPTIONS"
msgstr "MOŽNOSTI"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This program follows the usual GNU command line syntax, with long options "
"starting with two dashes (`--'). A summary of the options supported by "
"<command>kpat</command> is included below."
msgstr ""
"Ta program sledi običajni sintaksi ukazne vrstice GNU z dolgimi možnostmi, "
"ki se začnejo z dvema vezajema (`--'). Spodaj je vključen povzetek možnosti, "
"ki jih podpira <command>kpat</command>."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-h</option> <option>--help</option>"
msgstr "<option>-h</option> <option>--help</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "This lists the options available at the command line"
msgstr "To je seznam možnosti, ki so na voljo v ukazni vrstici"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-v</option> <option>--version</option>"
msgstr "<option>-v</option> <option>--version</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists version information for &kpatience;"
msgstr "Navaja informacije o različici za &kpatience;"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--solvegame</option> <replaceable> file</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--solvegame</option> <replaceable> file</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try to find a solution to the given savegame"
msgstr "Poskusite najti rešitev za dano shranjeno igro"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--solve</option> <replaceable> num</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--solve</option> <replaceable> num</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dealer to solve (debug)"
msgstr "Trgovec za rešitev (odpravljanje napak)"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--start</option> <replaceable> num</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--start</option> <replaceable> num</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game range start (default 0:INT_MAX)"
msgstr "Razpon začetka igre (privzeto 0:INT_MAX)"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--end</option> <replaceable> num</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--end</option> <replaceable> num</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game range end (default start:start if start given)"
msgstr "Konec obsega igre (privzeto start:start če dan start)"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--gametype</option> <replaceable> game</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--gametype</option> <replaceable> game</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Skip the selection screen and load a particular game type. Valid values are: "
"acesup, fortyeight, freecell, golf, grandfather, grandfathersclock, "
"normandy, klondike, mod3, simplesimon, spider, yukon"
msgstr ""
"Preskočite izbirni zaslon in naložite določeno vrsto igre. Veljavne "
"vrednosti so: acesup, fortyeight, freecell, golf, grandfather, "
"grandfathersclock, normandija, klondike, mod3, simplesimon, spider, yukon"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--testdir</option> <replaceable> directory</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--testdir</option> <replaceable> imenik</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Directory with test cases"
msgstr "Imenik s testnimi primeri"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "--generate"
msgstr "--generate"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generate random test cases"
msgstr "Ustvari naključne testne primere"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--author"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
